sentences.english: So he can't know, yet, that death doesn't really mean anything in comics.
sentences.chinese: 因而至今他也不知道死亡在漫画中没什么实际意义。

sentences.english: Zhou Lan did well and made no serious mistakes.
sentences.chinese: 周兰做得很好，基本上没什么差错。

sentences.english: It’s no big deal. I don’t mind helping you out.
sentences.chinese: 这没什么大不了的，我不介意帮助你摆脱困境。

sentences.english: Nothing pleased my mother more than to be told how good were her dishes.
sentences.chinese: 夸母亲的菜做得多好，没什么比这更使她高兴的了。

sentences.english: It is nothing special, it feels cold in my stomach," said Siti Qomariyah, who has been eating the snacks since she was a child.
sentences.chinese: 这没什么特别的，感觉胃里凉凉的。

sentences.english: The other, Albert Ho Chun-yan, is thus a no-hoper.
sentences.chinese: 如此看来，另一位参选者何俊仁是没什么希望了。

sentences.english: The front-of-house didn't think too much of it, especially the staff from overseas.
sentences.chinese: 前台都没什么感觉，特别是那些外籍员工。

sentences.english: Spring festival is over, nothing special happened. I am just sleeping, eating then eating, sleeping.
sentences.chinese: 春节假期过去了，没什么特别，只不过是吃吃睡睡。

sentences.english: No, I don't think I have any plans. Why do you ask?
sentences.chinese: 不忙，我想我没什么安排。你问来干嘛？

sentences.english: No task is beneath you when you have a servant’s heart.
sentences.chinese: 只有你有一颗仆人的心，就没什么工作你不愿作了。

sentences.english: But really there's nothing to be afraid of says Bogen.
sentences.chinese: 但是真的没什么好怕的，伯根说。

sentences.english: That will be fine, then, what about these chocolate candies.
sentences.chinese: 那就没什么关系。这些巧克力糖呢？

sentences.english: Except for the weapons and Japanese trucks, it could be 600 years ago.
sentences.chinese: 除了武器与日本卡车，它就跟600年前没什么两样。

sentences.english: He comes from a completely uncultured, lower middle-class family.
sentences.chinese: 他来自中下阶层一个根本没什么文化的家庭。

sentences.english: Nothing will be able to erase our wonderful memories, we will remember them forever.
sentences.chinese: 没什么能抹掉我们美好的记忆，我们会永远铭记在心。

sentences.english: Shen resists the frost wouldn t do him any good impression left early.
sentences.chinese: 沈傲霜对他没什么好印象早早的就走了。
